hip%26quot%3B%20so%20the%20actress%20would%20have%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to%20life%20as%20a%20royal%20before%20committing%20entirely.%20These%20claims%20came%20from%20royal%20author%20Rob%20Jobson%20in%20his%20upcoming%20book%2C%20%26quot%3BCatherine%2C%20the%20Princess%20of%20Wales%26quot%3B.%20He%20detailed%20how%20there%20were%20rifts%20in%20the%20Sussex%20and%20Wales'%20ties%20prior%20to%20Ms%20Markle%20formally%20joining%20the%20family%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWilliam%2C%20still%20concerned%20by%20the%20match%2C%20even%20sought%20assurances%20from%20the%20Queen%20that%20his%20brother's%20bride-to-be%20would%20not%20wear%20any%20jewellery%20in%20the%20collection%20once%20worn%20by%20Diana%2C%20Princess%20of%20Wales%2C%20even%20though%20his%20wife%20Catherine%20had%20been%20allowed%20to%20wear%20some%2C%20which%20would%20be%20due%20to%20her%20rank%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20book%2C%20the%20relationship%20between%20the%20brothers%20deteriorated%20even%20before%20Ms%20Markle%20became%20a%20member%20of%20the%20royal%20family.%20Mr%20Jobson%20said%20that%20William%20and%20Kate%20Middleton%20expressed%20concern%20about%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20Harry%20and%20Ms%20Markle%20were%20progressing%2C%20which%20only%20made%20their%20already%20tumultuous%20relationship%20worse%20when%20Harry%20brought%20the%20former%20actress%20to%20meet%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20author%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BHarry%20claimed%20that%20the%20goodwill%20from%20William%20and%20Catherine%20disappeared%20long%20before%20the%20build-up%20to%20his%20wedding.%20William%20had%20confided%20to%20his%20brother%20that%20he%20believed%20it%20would%20be%20better%20to%20give%20Meghan%20more%20time%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20royal%20way%20of%20life%20and%20suggested%20he%20cool%20the%20relationship.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHarry%20felt%20affronted%20and%20judged%20it%20to%20be%20an%20insult.%20As%20a%20direct%20result%2C%20his%20relationship%20with%20his%20brother%20deteriorated%20fast.%20According%20to%20Harry's%20book%20'Spare%2C'%20William%20physically%20attacked%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20book's%20other%20shocking%20revelations%20included%20that%20Ms%20Markle's%20relationship%20with%20Prince%20William%20and%20Princess%20of%20Wales%20didn't%20start%20out%20well%20because%20she%20%26quot%3Bignored%20the%20royal%20hierarchy.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20not%20so%20much%20stepped%20on%20royal%20toes%20as%20stamped%20on%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jobson%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Meghan%2C%20who%20had%20forgotten%20her%20lip%20gloss%2C%20asked%20to%20borrow%20Catherine's%2C%20the%20duchess%20was%20'taken%20aback'%20but%20reluctantly%20handed%20it%20to%20her.%20According%20to%20Harry%2C%20she%20'grimaced'%20after%20Meghan%20had%20squeezed%20some%20onto%20her%20finger%20and%20applied%20it%20to%20her%20lips%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20when%20Prince%20Harry's%20memoir%20'Spare'%20was%20released%2C%20it%20shocked%20the%20world.%20The%20book%20talked%20about%20the%20extent%20of%20division%20between%20Harry%20and%20his%20brother%20Prince%20William.%20Some%20of%20the%20revelations%20included%20how%20Prince%20William%2C%20heir%20to%20the%20British%20royal%20throne%2C%20allegedly%20pushed%20Harry%20to%20the%20ground%20in%202019%20and%20how%20the%20once-close%20brothers%20persuaded%20their%20father%20not%20to%20marry%20the%20Queen%20Consort%2C%20Camilla.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722392640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fkqgq84v8_prince-william-banned-meghan-markle-from-wearing-princess-dianas-jewellery_625x300_31_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fprince-william-banned-meghan-markle-from-wearing-princess-dianas-jewellery-reveals-new-book-6227807%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According