al%20run%20in%20the%20ongoing%20Paris%20Olympics.%20The%20star%20markswoman%20first%20clinched%20a%20historic%20bronze%20in%20the%20women's%2010m%20air%20pistol%20on%20July%2028.%20She%20became%20the%20first%20woman%20shooter%20from%20India%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20Manu%20bagged%20the%20same%20honour%20in%20the%20mixed%20team%2010m%20air%20pistol%20event%2C%20becoming%20the%20first-ever%20athlete%20from%20independent%20India%20to%20have%20won%20two%20medals%20in%20a%20single%20edition%20of%20the%20Olympics.%20Manu%20has%20now%20become%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20budding%20athletes%20with%20her%20achievements%20and%20her%20recent%20revelation%20in%20an%20interview%20further%20lifts%20her%20stature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20known%20the%20greats%20in%20Indian%20sports%20history.%20In%20my%20time%2C%20I%20have%20always%20known%20(PV)%20Sindhu%20and%20Neeraj%20(Chopra).%20I%20have%20always%20appreciated%20them%20for%20their%20hardwork.%20There%20was%20this%20one%20time%20when%20I%20made%20a%20fake%20profile%20to%20defend%20Sindhu.%20Some%20haters%20commented%20and%20I%20got%20so%20triggered%20that%20I%20made%20a%20fake%20account%20to%20defend%20her%20on%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Manu%20Bhaker%20told%20Sportstar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20Bhaker's%20revelation%20on%20X%2C%20Sindhu%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BHaha%20what%20a%20sweetheart!!!%20Welcome%20to%20the%202%20Olympic%20medal%20club%20Manu!!%20Way%20to%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20twice%20as%20nice%20for%20Manu%20Bhaker%20as%20she%20clinched%20a%20history-making%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20bronze%20with%20Sarabjot%20Singh%20in%20the%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20joining%20the%20league%20of%20India's%20greatest%20athletes%20in%20a%20span%20of%2072%20hours%20by%20being%20the%20driving%20force%20of%20the%20country's%20campaign%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20good%20124%20years%20after%20British-Indian%20Norman%20Pritchard%20won%20silver%20medals%20in%20200m%20sprint%20and%20200m%20hurdles%2C%20incidentally%20also%20in%20a%20Paris%20edition%20of%20the%20Games%2C%20Bhaker%20became%20the%20first%20athlete%20in%20post-independent%20India%20to%20snare%20two%20individual%20medals%20in%20the%20same%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhaker%20combined%20with%20an%20equally%20unruffled%20Sarabjot%20in%20the%2010m%20air%20pistol%20mixed%20team%20bronze%20and%20gave%20a%20superb%20demonstration%20of%20how%20to%20control%20nerves%20in%20a%20high-pressure%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20pair%20defeated%20the%20Korean%20duo%20of%20Lee%20Wonoho%20and%20Oh%20Yeh%20Jin%2016-10.%20It%20just%20added%20to%20Bhaker's%20growth%20story%20as%20she%20completely%20wiped%20off%20the%20memories%20of%20a%20horrendous%20Olympic%20debut%20in%20Tokyo%202020%20where%20her%20pistol%20malfunctioned%20leaving%20her%20in%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20it's%20not%20over%20yet.%20She%20remains%20in%20contention%20for%20another%20podium%20finish%20--%20in%20the%2025m%20sports%20pistol%20event%2C%20the%20qualification%20for%20which%20will%20take%20place%20on%20August%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20is%20a%20massive%20achievement%20for%20women's%20sport%20in%20the%20country%2C%20Tuesday's%20medal%20was%20also%20redemption%20for%20Sarabjot%2C%20who%20had%20failed%20to%20make%20the%20men's%2010m%20air%20pistol%20final%2C%20finishing%20ninth%20on%20Saturday%20with%20a%20score%20of%20577.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BActually%20we%20can't%20control%20(what%20the%20rivals%20will%20do)%2C%20we%20can%20do%20what%20is%20in%20our%20hand%2C%20me%20and%20my%20partner%20thought%20let's%20just%20try%20our%20best%20and%20we%20will%20keep%20fighting%20till%20the%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Bhaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbala%20shooter%20Sarabjot%2C%20who%20passed%20through%20a%20difficult%20phase%20trying%20to%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20the%20disappointment%20of%20the%20individual%20competition%20just%20three%20days%20ba