ider.com%2Findonesia-bali-tourist-mistake-travel-guide-local-tips-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBali%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Cynthia%2C%20in%20September%202008.%20The%20school%20has%20since%20expanded%20to%20new%20campuses%20in%20New%20Zealand%20and%20South%20Africa%20with%20a%20total%20global%20enrollment%20of%20just%20under%201%2C000%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20May%202021%2C%20the%20school%20has%20been%20managed%20by%20Education%20in%20Motion%2C%20a%20Singapore-based%20education%20company%2C%20although%20the%20Hardys%20are%20still%20involved%20as%20ambassadors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20getting%20up%20and%20telling%20the%20family%2C%20'We're%20moving%20to%20Bali%20for%20the%20Green%20School%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jackie%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20here%20we%20are.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenschool.org%2Fbali%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2024%2F02%2FGSB_Enrolment___Admissions_Policy_2024-25.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eapplication%20process%3C%2Fa%3E%20varies%20depending%20on%20which%20grade%20potential%20students%20are%20enrolling%20in.%20Those%20applying%20for%20primary%20school%20need%20to%20submit%20school%20reports%2C%20teacher%20recommendations%2C%20and%20a%20video%20as%20part%20of%20their%20application.%20Those%20applying%20for%20middle%20school%20need%20an%20essay%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20while%20those%20applying%20for%20high%20school%20have%20to%20sit%20for%20an%20interview%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20kids%20smiling%20widely%20for%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669779639caa6ed01e023bfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20three%20siblings%20attend%20Green%20School%20in%20Bali.%3Cp%3EJackie%20Easthope%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20since%20Jackie%20moved%20to%20Bali%20with%20her%20three%20kids%3A%20Mila%2C%2015%3B%20Kingston%2C%2013%3B%20and%20Indy%2C%209.%20They%20live%20in%20a%20rented%20house%20in%20Beraban%2C%20located%20north%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbali-digital-nomad-lifestyle-price-budget-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanggu%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20views%20of%20rice%20paddies.%20Her%20husband%20splits%20his%20time%20between%20New%20Zealand%20and%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20family's%20decision%20to%20school%20their%20children%20in%20Bali%20took%20a%20few%20years%20of%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20have%20three%20kids%2C%20it%20has%20to%20work%20for%20all%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20worried%20about%20the%20two%20girls.%20I%20knew%20their%20personalities%20would%20suit%20the%20Green%20School%2C%20but%20I%20was%20worried%20about%20my%20son%20Kingston%20because%20he%20loves%20structure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a2120c9-250e-42db-ad8c-10de8679a8e8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProject-based%20learning%2C%20smaller%20class%20sizes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mila%2C%20school%20in%20Bali%20is%20a%20whole%20new%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20New%20Zealand%2C%20we%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20big%20classes.%20You%20don't%20really%20get%20to%20ask%20many%20questions%3B%20you%20just%20listen%20and%20then%20do%20your%20worksheet%2C%26quot%3B%20Mila%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20since%20I'm%20dyslexic%2C%20it%20was%20really%20hard%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20red%20dress%20and%20a%20young%20girl%20in%20a%20blue%20dress%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bamboo%20building%20in%20Bali.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66977a829caa6ed01e023c13%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20says%20she%20noticed%20her%20daughter%20Mila%20start%20to%20flourish%20in%20school%20after%20joining%20Green%20School.%3Cp%3EJackie%20Easthope%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20she%20often%20got%20put%20into%20a%20lower%20learning%20program%20than%20her%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20Bali%2C%20Mila%20said%20she%20got%20personalized%20attention%20from%20her%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20teachers%20would%20move%20around%20the%20classroom%2C%20ask%20me%20questions%2C%20and%20point%20me%20out%20individually.%20Since%20it%20was%20a%2010-person%20classroom%2C%20I%20actually%20understood%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20school's%20teaching%20model%20involves%20using%20practical%20examples%2C%20Mads%20Hedegaard%2C%20the%20director%20of%20admission%2C%20marketing%2C%20and%20communication%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20be%20a%20giant%20coconut%20slingshot%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20calculate%20trajectories%2C%20our%20seed-to-table%20cafe%20where%20the%20youngest%20students%20learn%20how%20to%20grow%20vegetables%2C%20and%20our%20middle%20schoolers%20learn%20entrepreneurship%20by%20running%20the%20cafe%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20Hedegaard%20said.%20%26quot%3BOr%20it%20can%20be%20hands-on%20projects%20like%20building%20a%20yurt%20to%20learn%20math%2C%20physics%2C%20and%20practical%20arts%20at%20the%20same%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Mila%20recently%20completed%20a%20project%20in%20collaboration%20with%20a%20local%20women's%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20my%20own%20artwork%20to%20raise%20awareness%20of%20domestic%20violence%2C%20sold%20it%2C%20and%20then%20made%20enough%20money%20to%20help%20them%20with%20appliances%20in%20the%20shelter%2C%26quot%3B%20Mila%20said.%20After%20completing%20it%2C%20she%20had%20to%20give%20a%20presentation%20about%20her%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232090d2b-4a98-4d9c-9be7-e8d7883a2c41%5C%22%3EA%20different%20grading%20system%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenschool.org%2Fbali%2Fstudent-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClassrooms%20at%20the%20Green%20School%20don't%20have%20walls%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Students%20learn%20about%20the%20natural%20world%2C%20care%20for%20animals%2C%20and%20grow%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20high-school-level%20students%20receive%20grades%20at%20the%20Green%20School%3B%20younger%20students%20at%20the%20primary%20and%20middle%20school%20levels%20get%20a%20progress%20report%20instead%2C%20Hedegaard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20young%20students%20sitting%20at%20their%20wooden%20desks%20in%20a%20bamboo%20school%20building%20in%20Bali.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66977b635439fb59cebdfc6b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClassrooms%20in%20the%20Green%20School%20don't%20have%20walls%2C%20and%20the%20curriculum%20emphasizes%20teaching%20students%20the%20importance%20of%20living%20sustainably.%3Cp%3EPutu%20Sayoga%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHigh-school%20students'%20grades%20account%20not%20just%20for%20their%20test%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Escores%20but%20also%20for%20their%20participation%20and%20engagement%20in%20class%2C%20Mila%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudents%20also%20have%20the%20freedom%20to%20take%20electives%20that%20interest%20them%2C%20and%20those%20in%20higher%20levels%20can%20even%20introduce%20their%20own%20classes%20if%20they%20get%20a%20teacher%20to%20sign%20off%20on%20it%2C%20Mila%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20possible%20as%20long%20as%20the%20student%20provides%20a%20clear%20overview%20of%20learning%20outcomes%20and%20the%20course%20is%20related%20to%20one%20of%20the%20credit%20areas%20stipulated%20by%20the%20school%2C%20Hedegaard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMila's%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20dance%20class%20because%20she%20loves%20dancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20I%20love%20about%20Green%20School%20is%20that%20I%20think%20the%20kids%20get%20to%20explore%20their%20passions%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20and%20a%20young%20girl%20standing%20side%20by%20side%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bamboo%20school%20building%20in%20Bali.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a870b9aab37011780b889f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJackie%20Easthope%20and%20her%20daughter%20Mila%20at%20the%20Green%20School%20in%20Bali%2C%20Indonesia.%3Cp%3EJackie%20Easthope%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20school%20does%20support%20students%20who%20wish%20to%20take%20the%20SATs%20or%20other%20kinds%20of%20exams%20for%20university%20admission%2C%20Jackie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdirectory.acswasc.org%2Fnew%2Fdirectory-searchlist.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20Western%20Associates%20of%20Schools%20and%20Colleges%20(WASC)%20%E2%80%94%20an%20institution%20that%20accredits%20high%20schools%20in%20the%20US%20%E2%80%94%20shows%20that%20Green%20School%20is%20also%20accredited%20under%20the%20commission.%20A%20WASC%20representative%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20school%20has%20been%20accredited%20since%20the%202016-2017%20school%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20GPA%20averages%20earned%20with%20our%20school%20can%20also%20be%20transformed%20into%20many%20other%20schooling%20systems%20globally%2C%26quot%3B%20Hedegaard%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Green%20School%20in%20Bali%20currently%20has%20510%20students%20enrolled%20across%2039%20nationalities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20around%2070%20Indonesian%20students%20at%20Green%20School%20Bali%2C%20of%20which%20half%20are%20on%20full%20scholarships%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275db838a-f4ee-4282-8d40-f003ceaad58c%5C%22%3EA%20pricey%20education%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20of%20this%20comes%20at%20a%20hefty%20price%20tag%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.greenschool.org%2Fbali%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F2%2F2023%2F02%2FGSB-ADMISSIONS-Tuition-Fees-Schedule-2023-24.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYearly%20tuition%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20start%20from%20117.95%20million%20Indonesian%20Rupiah%2C%20or%20%247%2C260%2C%20for%20pre-K%20students%20and%20can%20go%20up%20to%20302%2C1%20million%20Indonesian%20Rupiah%2C%20or%20%2418%2C650%2C%20for%20Grade%2011%20and%2012%20high%20school%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20those%20prices%20might%20not%20shock%20Westerners%20used%20to%20paying%20for%20private%20schools%20in%20major%2C%20developed%20cities%2C%20they%20are%20considered%20high%20for%20the%20island%20of%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20eating%20lunch%20at%20Green%20School%20Bali%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669f681080d4d5da13d61f4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYearly%20tuition%20fees%20at%20Green%20School%20Bali%20do%20not%20come%20cheap.%3Cp%3EPutu%20Sayoga%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20average%20monthly%20net%20wage%20in%20Bali%20is%20about%203.04%20million%20Indonesian%20rupiah%2C%20or%20%24187.75%2C%20per%20the%20latest%20February%202019%20data%20from%20data%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ceicdata.com%2Fen%2Findonesia%2Fmonthly-average-wage-net-by-province%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEIC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20tuition%20fees%20at%20Green%20School%20Bali%20are%20comparable%20to%20those%20of%20other%20international%20schools%20on%20the%20island.%20Yearly%20tuition%20fees%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ccsbali.com%2Fadmissions%2Ffees%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanggu%20Community%20School%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0start%20at%20105%20million%20Indonesian%20Rupiah%20for%20preschool%20and%20go%20up%20to%20245%20million%20Indonesian%20Rupiah%20for%20year%2012%20and%20year%2013%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fees%20are%20not%20high%20compared%20to%20other%20international%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20Hedegaard%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20many%20parents%20experience%20a%20decline%20in%20fees%20moving%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a3ce2ab-a442-4f22-ba47-b20adaf65b3b%5C%22%3EAdjusting%20to%20life%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJackie%20said%20that%20although%20her%20daughters%20easily%20settled%20into%20life%20in%20Bali%2C%20her%20son%20needed%20a%20longer%20adjustment%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20came%20here%2C%20my%20boy%20%E2%80%94%20up%20until%20the%20end%20%E2%80%94%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave%20New%20Zealand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20first%20six%20months%20after%20moving%20to%20Bali%20was%20a%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20day%2C%20I'd%20ask%20him%2C%20'How%20was%20school%3F'%20And%20he%20would%20say%2C%20'I%20hate%20it%2C%20I%20hate%20that%20you%20brought%20me%20here%2C'%26quot%3B%20Jackie%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20the%20thing%20is%2C%20so%20many%20families%20coming%20to%20Green%20School%20go%20through%20this.%20They'll%20have%20one%20child%20who%20hates%20it.%20And%20I'm%20always%20saying%20to%20them%2C%20give%20it%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20reason%2C%20one%20day%2C%20it%20was%20like%20a%20switch%20went%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20he%20made%20great%20friends%2C%20and%20he%20didn't%20hate%20school.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285d1882a-4988-4e6b-a9e4-0f407d0af40f%5C%22%3ELess%20stress%2C%20more%20confidence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mila%2C%20the%20educational%20environment%20at%20the%20Green%20School%20has%20helped%20her%20grow%20into%20a%20more%20confident%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20learned%20how%20to%20present%20myself%20and%20communicate%20my%20ideas%20with%20others%2C%20especially%20when%20speaking%20to%20adults%20or%20in%20front%20of%20a%20camera%2C%26quot%3B%20Mila%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn't%20feel%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20academic%20pressure%20that%20she%20did%20back%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTests%20are%20so%20much%20more%20daunting%2C%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20them%20here.%20It's%20mostly%20presentations%20and%20you%20learn%20after%20a%20few%20years%20how%20to%20be%20confident%20and%20not%20really%20stress%20over%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Mila%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20take%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20classes%2C%20and%20I%20get%20to%20try%20a%20lot%20of%20things.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-moves-family-bali-children-green-school-alternative-education-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722384842000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669ff887fb2b6bedb059b6c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-moves-family-bali-children-green-school-alternative-education-2024-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BKids%20are%20not%20scared%20of%20their%20teachers.%20They%20respect%20them%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20where%20they%20feel%20like%20they%20can't%20ask%20their%20teachers%20any%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20Jackie%20Easthope%20told%20BI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22agoh%40businessinsider.com%20(Amanda%20Goh)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-moves-family-bali-children-green-school-alternative-education-2024-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Simone%20Biles%20Completes%20Her%20%E2%80%98Redemption%20Tour%E2%80%99%20at%20Paris%