h%20Hall%2C%20and%20her%20children%20in%20January%202023.%3Cp%3EJon%20Kopaloff%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Feld%20Entertainment%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20want%20to%20have%20a%20situation%20where%20there%20is%20a%20misunderstanding%20or%20any%20conflict%2C%20especially%20in%20front%20of%20my%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20RFO%2C%20Christina%20said%20that%20although%20the%20Newport%20Beach%20home%20is%20legally%20owned%20by%20both%20herself%20and%20Josh%2C%20it%20was%20purchased%20with%20money%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20her%20previous%20residence%20in%20Dana%20Point%2C%20California.%20She%20added%20that%20Josh%20came%20to%20the%20home%20unscheduled%20and%20%26quot%3Btook%20items%26quot%3B%20after%20their%20separation%20on%20July%207%20and%20that%20he%20plugged%20in%20security%20cameras%20Christina%20intentionally%20unplugged%20per%20a%20request%20from%20his%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJosh's%20attorney%20sent%20a%20letter%20demanding%20that%20I%20preserve%20electronic%20evidence%20without%20it%20being%20automatically%20deleted%2C%20so%20I%20unplugged%20cameras%20so%20the%20system%20would%20not%20automatically%20overwrite%20the%20hard%20drive%2C%26quot%3B%20Christina%20wrote%20in%20her%20filing.%20%26quot%3BEach%20time%20Josh%20has%20returned%20to%20the%20house%20he%20has%20plugged%20the%20cameras%20back%20in%2C%20which%20would%20allow%20him%20to%20keep%20me%20and%20my%20children%20under%20surveillance.%20I%20object%20to%20him%20having%20that%20access%20into%20my%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223522c1bb-2a3a-44cc-a6ed-fb64b119b358%5C%22%3EChristina%20also%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20make%20Josh%20return%20%2435%2C000%20to%20her%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20said%20in%20the%20same%20filing%20that%20she%20wanted%20the%20court%20to%20instruct%20Josh%20to%20return%20%2435%2C000%20that%20she%20says%20he%20transferred%20on%20July%208%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20my%20authorization%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20personal%20account%20he%20used%20before%20their%20marriage.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20July%2021%2C%202024%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20on%20July%208%2C%202024%2C%20which%20is%20the%20day%20after%20I%20communicated%20to%20Josh%20that%20I%20would%20be%20filing%20for%20dissolution%2C%20Josh%20contacted%20my%20professional%20property%20manager%20via%20text%20and%20stated%20'Hi.%20For%20June%20payments%2C%20can%20we%20please%20get%20it%20sent%20to%20a%20different%20account%20when%20it's%20time%3F%20Thank%20you%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20attaching%20a%20screenshot%20of%20the%20message%20to%20the%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20statement%20'can%20we%20please'%20is%20not%20accurate%20as%20I%20had%20no%20personal%20contact%20with%20Josh%20on%20July%208%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20Christina%20said%20in%20the%20RFO.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20have%20asked%20him%20to%20send%20himself%20my%20money%20the%20day%20after%20I%20told%20him%20we%20are%20getting%20divorced.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christina%20Hall%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20a%20blue%20backdrop.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669829de49138fa6f6e33b94%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222735%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChristina%20Hall%20in%202019.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Buchan%2FVariety%2FPenske%20Media%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20also%20addressed%20Josh's%20request%20for%20spousal%20support%20in%20her%20RFO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20that%20at%20some%20point%20this%20Court%20may%20require%20that%20I%20pay%20some%20spousal%20support%20to%20Josh%20and%20reasonable%20attorney's%20fees%20to%20his%20counsel%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20it%20is%20my%20belief%20that%20this%20is%20a%20simple%20case%20with%20straightforward%20accounting%20over%20a%20short%20time%20period%2C%20any%20fees%20and%20costs%20should%20be%20minimal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20all%20hard-working%20mothers%2C%20my%20life%20revolves%20around%20my%20children%20and%20my%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20my%20understanding%20that%20Josh%20has%20his%20own%20income%20and%20therefore%20he%20should%20not%20need%20any%20spousal%20support%20from%20me.%20He%20has%20sufficient%20assets%20of%20his%20own%20to%20pay%20his%20own%20attorney's%20fees%20and%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bshocked%20and%20concerned%26quot%3B%20that%20he%20transferred%20%2435%2C000%20of%20her%20%26quot%3Bseparate%20property%20money%26quot%3B%20to%20his%20personal%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20this%20is%20the%20same%20date%20he%20now%20alleges%20to%20be%20our%20date%20of%20separation%2C%20even%20though%20it%20is%20actually%20July%2007%2C%202024%2C%20makes%20it%20clear%20why%20he%20chose%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Christina%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20me%20wonder%20what%20else%20I%20am%20not%20aware%20of%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20his%20financial%20situation%20and%20that%20is%20why%20I%20am%20having%20a%20full%20forensic%20accounting%20performed%20for%20the%20entire%20term%20of%20our%20marriage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20has%20not%20filed%20a%20response%20to%20Christina's%20RFO.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Superior%20Court%20of%20Orange%20County%2C%20the%20Halls%20have%20a%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20October%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a758d467-6072-452e-884c-279a52e0d971%5C%22%3EChristina%20took%20to%20social%20media%20to%20open%20up%20about%20the%20separation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChristina%20shared%20a%20series%20of%20Instagram%20stories%20about%20her%20separation%20from%20Josh%20on%20Thursday%20and%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20here%20waiting%20for%20the%20typical%20Hired%20PR%20speech%20of%20'how%20I%20was%20blindsided%20and%20how%20I'm%2