ssinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fhilton-honors-american-express-surpass-card-review%5C%22%3EHilton%20Honors%20American%20Express%20Surpass%C2%AE%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20earn%20one%20by%20spending%20%2415%2C000%20on%20the%20card%20in%20a%20calendar%20year.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20each%20carry%20both%20the%20Aspire%20and%20the%20Surpass%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20rack%20up%20four%20certificates%20each%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20spotted%20three%20consecutive%20nights%20available%20at%20standard%20rates%20at%20Pedregal%20this%20past%20May%2C%20I%20quickly%20applied%20three%20certificates%20to%20maximize%20their%20value.%20Doing%20so%20allowed%20me%20to%20hang%20onto%20360%2C000%20Hilton%20points%20%E2%80%94%20which%20I%20figured%20I%20could%20use%20in%20part%20for%20two%20more%20nights%20at%20a%20less-expensive%20Hilton%20property%20%E2%80%94%20and%20book%20a%20room%20that%20would%20have%20cost%20over%20%245%2C700%20for%20three%20nights%20in%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20going%20ahead%20and%20locking%20in%20the%20last%20two%20nights%20elsewhere%2C%20though%2C%20I%20took%20a%20gamble.%20Knowing%20that%20many%20Hilton%20hotels%20%E2%80%94%20Pedregal%20included%20%E2%80%94%20tend%20to%20make%20rooms%20available%20at%20standard%20rates%20at%20the%20last%20minute%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20hold%20off%20on%20booking%20anything%20and%20instead%20checked%20Pedregal's%20availability%20daily.%20My%20persistence%20paid%20off%3A%20On%20the%20flight%20to%20Mexico%2C%20the%20last%20two%20nights%20finally%20opened%20up%20at%20standard%20rates%2C%20and%20I%20was%20able%20to%20use%20our%20last%20certificate%20and%20120%2C000%20points%20to%20grab%20them.%20By%20the%20time%20we%20arrived%20at%20the%20hotel%2C%20we%20were%20all%20set%20for%20a%20free%20five-night%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E2.%20We%20used%20credits%20to%20cover%20airfare%2C%20taxes%20and%20fees%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20United%20flights%20to%20and%20from%20Mexico%2C%20and%20in%20order%20t