r.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%23rating-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20credit%20cards%20to%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22829%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jason%20Steele%20is%20a%20freelance%20contributor%20for%20Business%20Insider's%20personal%20finance%20division.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a021da80d4d5da13d6834a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Jason%20Steele.%3Cp%3EJason%20Steele%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20daughter%20wanted%20to%20visit%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20colleges%20on%20the%20East%20Coast%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETo%20save%20money%2C%20we%20went%20to%20several%20schools%20in%20one%20trip%20%E2%80%94%20and%20used%20credit%20card%20rewards%20to%20pay.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWe%20were%20able%20to%20go%20on%20several%20tours%20and%20make%20several%20other%20fun%20stops%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20doesn't%20seem%20that%20long%20ago%20that%20our%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20but%20somehow%20I%20found%20myself%20planning%20a%20trip%20to%20visit%20prospective%20colleges%20with%20her%20last%20spring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20living%20her%20entire%20life%20within%20a%20mile%20of%20where%20she%20was%20born%20in%20Denver%2C%20it%20was%20no%20surprise%20that%20this%20high-achieving%20child%20wants%20to%20consider%20colleges%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20paid%20my%20first%20tuition%20bill%2C%20I%20really%20didn't%20want%20to%20spend%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20just%20to%20visit%20some%20schools%20that%20she%20might%20want%20to%20apply%20to.%20Thankfully%2C%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fbest-rewards-credit-cards%5C%22%3Erewards%20credit%20cards%3