20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fchase-ink-business-preferred-card-review%5C%22%3EInk%20Business%20Preferred%C2%AE%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20the%20rewards%20we%20earn%20can%20be%20combined%20with%20our%20Chase%20Sapphire%20Reserve%20and%20Ink%20Business%20Preferred%20accounts%2C%20allowing%20us%20to%20transfer%20them%20to%20airline%20miles%20and%20hotel%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I%20hold%20a%20Southwest%20Airlines%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20which%20I%20earned%20from%20signing%20up%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fsouthwest-rapid-rewards-plus-credit-card-review%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fsouthwest-performance-business-credit-card-review%5C%22%3ESouthwest%C2%AE%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Performance%20Business%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20combined%20new%20account%20bonuses%20are%20enough%20to%20earn%20the%20necessary%20points%2C%20and%20I%20can%20add%20my%20daughter%20to%20any%20flight%20I%20book%2C%20cutting%20the%20number%20of%20points%20needed%20for%20our%20flights%20in%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStarting%20our%20trip%20in%20Florida%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20left%20Denver%20on%20a%20Sunday%20afternoon%20and%20arrived%20in%20Orlando%20that%20night.%20We%20were%20able%20to%20book%20an%20award%20night%20stay%20at%20the%20Hyatt%20House%20by%20Orlando%20Airport.%20I%20use%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fworld-of-hyatt-credit-card-review%5C%22%3EWorld%20Of%20Hyatt%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-cards%2Fworld-of-hyatt-business-credit-card-review%5C%22%3EWorld%20of%20Hyatt%20Business%20Credit