%20a%2060-year-old%20woman%20to%20death%20at%20his%20home%20and%20grievously%20injured%20her%20daughter%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20intervene.%20The%20man%20is%20a%20relative%20of%20the%20women%20and%20residents%20said%20not%20only%20did%20he%20show%20no%20remorse%20but%20also%20publicly%20threatened%20the%20injured%20woman%20while%20she%20was%20bleeding%20and%20trying%20to%20run%20for%20her%20life.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeighbours%20said%20when%20they%20heard%20a%20commotion%20in%20one%20of%20the%20houses%20in%20Tilak%20Nagar's%20Sant%20Garh%20area%2C%20they%20assumed%20it%20was%20a%20familial%20dispute.%20Nearly%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20a%20woman%20could%20be%20heard%20screaming%20loudly%20while%20another%20ran%20across%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20bleeding%20and%20begging%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attacker%2C%20who%20is%20on%20the%20run%2C%20has%20been%20identified%20as%20Rahul.%20The%20neighbours%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20living%20in%20the%20area%20with%20his%20parents%20and%20a%20younger%20brother%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%20and%20while%20the%20other%20members%20of%20the%20family%20were%20polite%20and%20never%20caused%20any%20trouble%2C%20Rahul%20was%20known%20for%20behaving%20like%20a%20goon%20and%20also%20stealing%20petrol%20from%20cars.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20heard%20the%20noise%20in%20one%20of%20the%20houses%2C%20we%20thought%20there%20was%20a%20dispute.%20Then%20we%20heard%20loud%20screams%20and%20we%20saw%20a%20woman%20with%20blood%20oozing%20out%20of%20her%20stomach%20running%20in%20the%20street%20with%20her%20children.%20Rahul%20also%20came%20out%20and%20he%20had%20a%20cellphone%20in%20his%20hand%2C%20which%20he%20handed%20to%20someone%20and%20asked%20them%20to%20give%20it%20to%20his%20mother.%20He%20did%20not%20look%20worried%20or%20remorseful%20at%20all%20and%20stood%20there%20talking%20to%20everyone%20for%20five%20minutes%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20neighbour%2C%20Paramjit%20Kaur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20as%20the%20woman%20kept%20screaming%2C%20he%20shouted%20after%20her%20and%20said%20I%20have%20already%20killed%20one%20woman%2C%20I%20will%20kill%20you%20too.%20The%20boy%20is%20an%20addict%20and%20he%20has%20thrown%20his%20weight%20around%20several%20times.%20He%20was%20neither%20afraid%20nor%20worried.%20We%20haven't%20seen%20the%20two%20women%20before.%20The%20police%20were%20informed%20and%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20police%20official%20said%20the%20woman%20who%20died%20has%20been%20identified%20as%2060-year-old%20Veena.%20%26quot%3BShe%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20Her%20daughter%2C%20Tanya%2C%20suffered%20severe%20injuries%20and%20has%20been%20admitted%20to%20the%20Guru%20Gobind%20Singh%20Government%20Hospital%20in%20Tilak%20Nagar.%20The%20women%20had%20gone%20to%20Rahul's%20house%20to%20discuss%20a%20personal%20issue%20and%20an%20argument%20broke%20out.%20The%20argument%20escalated%20and%20he%20stabbed%20them%20both%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20official%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722355200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fknchm4eg_tilak-nagar-murder_625x300_30_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-stabs-60-year-old-to-death-in-her-house-in-delhi-injures-daughter-6224810%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22West%20Delhi's%20Tilak%20Nagar%20witnessed%20a%20dastardly%20crime%20on%20Tuesday%20when%20a%2022-year-old%20man%20stabbed%20a%2060-year-old%20woman%20to%20death%20at%20her%20home%20and%20grievously%20injured%20her%20daughter%20when%20she%20tried%20to%20intervene.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-stabs-60-year-old-to-death-in-her-house-in-delhi-injures-daughter-6224810%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneighbour-stabs-60-year-old-to-death-in-her-hous