ual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Franjita3-1722346018.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359081%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ranjita%20Gogoi%20won%20a%20bronze%20and%20a%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%20Asia%20Pacific%20Masters%20Games%202023%20held%20in%20South%20Korea.%20Called%20the%20'Iron%20Lady'%20of%20Assam%2C%20she%20excels%20in%20athletics%2C%20arm%20wrestling%20and%20powerlifting%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359081%2Franjita-gogoi-assam-swimming-athlete-senior-citizen-champion-international-armwrestling-powerlifting-competition%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20Firms%20Told%20To%20Be%20Careful%20While%20Doing%20Business%20With%20Chinese%20Firms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20embassy%20in%20Beijing%20has%20issued%20an%20advisory%20asking%20Indian%20small%20and%20medium%20enterprises%20(SMEs)%20to%20take%20certain%20precautions%20before%20doing%20any%20business%20with%20Chinese%20companies%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20states%20that%20these%20precautions%20are%20needed%20as%20the%20Embassy%20has%20regularly%20come%20across%20several%20problems%20faced%20by%20Indian%20companies%20doing%20business%20with%20Chinese%20entities%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20recommends%20that%20before%20doing%20business%20with%20any%20Chinese%20entity%2C%20Indian%20companies%20write%20to%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20(com.beijing%40mea.gov.in%2C%20ccom.beijing%40mea.gov.in)%20or%20Indian%20Consulates%20at%20Shanghai%20(hoc.shanghai%40mea.gov.in)%2C%20Guangzhou%20(com.guangzhou%40mea.gov.in)%20and%20Hong%20Kong%20(commerce.hongkong%40mea.gov.in)%20to%20verify%20the%20credentials%20of%20the%20entity.%20The%20respective%20Mission%20will%20respond%20in%204-5%20working%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20case%20of%20large%20transactions%2C%20it%20is%20highly%20recommended%20that%20Indian%20companies%20consult%20a%20Business%20Service%20Company%20which%20can%20provide%20a%20report%20on%20the%20business%20transparency%2C%20financial%20health%2C%20reputation%2C%20reliability%20and%20credentials%20of%20the%20Chinese%20entity%2C%20the%20advisory%20further%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20also%20recommends%20that%20before%20doing%20business%20with%20any%20Chinese%20entity%2C%20Indian%20companies%20collect%20and%20retain%20copies%20of%20both%20the%20Resident%20Identity%20Card%20(Chinese%20Identity%20Number)%20and%20passport%20of%20the%20proprietor%20and%20other%20responsible%20interlocutor(s)%20of%20the%20Chinese%20entity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20has%20observed%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20trade%20dispute%20cases%20involve%20companies%20registered%20in%20Shandong%2C%20Hebei%2C%20Guangdong%2C%20Jiangsu%20and%20Zhejiang%20provinces.%20Therefore%2C%20Indian%20companies%20are%20advised%20to%20take%20extra%20precautions%20before%20trading%20with%20companies%20from%20these%20provinces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20advisory%20that%20has%20been%20posted%20by%20the%20Indian%20embassy%20on%20X%20also%20has%20some%20annexure%20documents%20which%20businesses%20need%20to%20look%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnexure%201%20contains%20a%20list%20of%20typical%20problems%20that%20Indian%20companies%20face.%20It%20also%20contains%20a%20checklist%20of%20precautions%20that%20Indian%20companies%20are%20advised%20to%20take%20while%20dealing%20with%20Chinese%20entities.%20Annexure%202%20contains%20descriptive%20accounts%20of%20typical%20modus%20operandi%20adopted%20by%20offending%20Chinese%20entities%20while%20Annexure%203%20contains%20a%20list%20of%20Chinese%20entities%20involved%20in%20trade%20disputes%20with%20Indian%20companies%20from%202009%20to%20April%202024.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20ed