-mumbai-slums-feminist-icon-women-movement-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereaching%20out%20to%20help%20school%20dropouts%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Risia%20block%20restart%20their%20education.%20This%20was%20a%20godsend%20opportunity%20for%20Rachna%20to%20not%20just%20resume%20her%20studies%20but%20also%20to%20convince%20her%20parents%20to%20drop%20her%20marriage%20plans.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20she%20was%20admitted%20into%20college%20through%20Project%20Lehar%2C%20she%20was%20also%20counseled%20on%20entrepreneurial%20and%20career%20prospects.%20One%20such%20session%20on%20wheat%20stalk%20painting%20was%20to%20change%20her%20life%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWheat%20stalk%20painting%2C%20a%20traditional%20art%20form%20of%20Bahraich%2C%20is%20a%20laborious%20and%20time%20consuming%20process.%20It%20is%20created%20by%20cutting%20wheat%20stalks%20into%20fine%20sections%20to%20craft%20intricate%20designs%20on%20cloth%20using%20sharp-edged%20blades%20and%20razors.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Some%20of%20Rachna's%20beautiful%20paintings%20made%20from%20wheat%20stalk.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2F16da3002-9bec-4787-82bb-10e845c9c0f2-1722256456-768x432.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetter