.%20I%20had%20to%20pay%20for%20water%2C%20with%20a%20lake%20right%20in%20my%20backyard%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dayanand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chitlapakkam%20Lake%2C%20which%20is%20about%20100%20years%20old%20according%20to%20the%20residents%2C%20was%20in%20a%20poor%20shape.%20This%20was%20highlighted%20every%20rainy%20season%2C%20according%20to%20Sunil%20Jayaram%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202015%20floods%2C%20when%20they%20analysed%20the%20root%20cause%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20they%20found%20the%20answer%20in%20this%20lake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20lake%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20total%20neglect.%20Garbage%20was%20dumped%20on%20one%20side%20and%20the%20entire%20lake%20was%20filled%20with%20hyacinths%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sunil.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChitlapakkam%20has%20had%20very%20strong%20citizens%20associations%20since%20the%20late%2080s%2F90s.%20L%20Sundararaman%2C%20President%2C%20Chitlapakkam%20Muthulakshmi%20Nagar%20Welfare%20Association%2C%20who%20moved%20here%20in%201987%2C%20remembers%20the%20lake%20having%20less%20water%20even%20at%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20catered%20to%20the%20agricultural%20lands%20in%20the%20area%20in%20its%20heyday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20urbanisation%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F296793%2Fex-army-officer-restores-stormwater-drains-bengaluru-rains-floods-water-logging-solution%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elake%20slowly%20lost%20its%20glory%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20when%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Housing%20Board%20(TNHB)%20tried%20to%20construct%20houses%20around%20the%20lake%2C%20associations%20similar%20to%20Sundararaman%E2%80%99s%20halted%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20formed%20a%20Coordination%20Committee%20of%20Chitlapakkam%20Associations%20with%20one%20of%20the%20major%20goals%20being%20preservation%20of%20the%20lake.%20We%20protested%20against%20the%20TNHB%E2%80%99s%20move%2C%20including%20forming%20human-chains%2C%20and%20successfully%20halted%20their%20construction%20plan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Chitlapakkam%20Lake%20Preservation%20Committee%20also%20successfully%20constructed%20a%20bund%20across%20the%20lake%20in%202000%2C%20adds%20the%20resident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEach%20resident%20contributed%20Rs%20100%20voluntarily%20to%20build%20the%20bund.%20The%20government%20contributed%20an%20equal%20amount%20and%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20major%20reasons%20for%20preserving%20the%20existing%20area%20of%20the%20lake%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20retired%20BSNL%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20478px)%20100vw%2C%20478px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-16-at-10.50.21-1721993489.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22478%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20protest%20conducted%20by%20Chitlapakkam%20residents%20in%20the%20early%202000s%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-16-at-10.50.21-1721993489.jpeg%20478w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-16-at-10.50.21-1721993489-300x202.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-16-at-10.50.21-1721993489-150x101.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358728%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20protest%20conducted%20by%20Chitlapakkam%20residents%20in%20the%20early%202000s%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20efforts%2C%20even%20in%202015%2C%20the%20lake%20was%20not%20able%20to%20fulfil%20its%20basic%20purpose%2C%20i.e.%20recharge%20groundwater.