.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETemperature%20%E2%80%93%20Can%20tolerate%20up%20to%2035%C2%B0C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20%E2%80%93%20Regular%20watering%20is%20required.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFertiliser%20%E2%80%93%20Add%20animal%20manure%20once%20in%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721986020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358530%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Growing%20fruit%20trees%20in%20pots%20presents%20a%20viable%20and%20delightful%20solution%20for%20those%20limited%20by%20small%20spaces%20and%20gardens.%20Here%20are%20five%20fruit%20trees%20that%20thrive%20in%20containers%20and%20demand%20minimal%20maintenance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358530%2Ffruit-trees-terrace-garden-small-spaces-sushma-reddy-tips-and-tricks-mango-dragon-fruit-orange%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kids%20to%20Senior%20Citizens%2C%20Anyone%20Can%20Use%20This%20Techie%E2%80%99s%20DIY%20Handloom%20Kit%20To%20Weave%20Fabric%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKalaiyarasi%20Ramachandran%20spent%20her%20childhood%20admiring%20the%20large%20handlooms%20in%20the%20quaint%20weavers%E2%80%99%20lanes%20of%20Salangapalayam%20village%20in%20Erode%20district%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20The%20rhythmic%20sound%20of%20looms%20and%20transformation%20of%20yarn%20into%20nine%20yards%20of%20sarees%20diligently%20woven%20by%20the%20weavers%20was%20magical%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20would%20carefully%20watch%20the%20fine%20threads%20being%20woven%20in%20the%20loom.%20We%20would%20fear%20sitting%20near%20the%20weavers%20as%20the%20work%20required%20focus%20and%20no%20distraction.%20I%20would%20be%20tasked%20with%20small%20works%20like%20rotating%20the%20spinning%20wheel.%20We%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%3Cem%3Eraatai%20%3C%2Fem%3E(spinning%20wheel)%20in%20our%20house%2C%20so%20I%20would%20sneak%20to%20the%20weavers%E2%80%99%20homes%20and%20admire%20the%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20grew%20up%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20went%20on%20to%20study%20computer%20science%20and%20secured%20a%20well-paying%20job%20at%20an%20IT%20company%20in%20Chennai%20as%20a%20developer.%20A%20turning%20point%20came%20in%20her%20life%20when%20she%20came%20back%20to%20her%20hometown%20during%20her%20second%20maternity%20leave%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20noticed%20that%20the%20looms%20in%20my%20hometown%20had%20reduced%20from%207%2C500%20to%20only%202%2C500.%20A%20lot%20of%20weavers%20migrated%20to%20other%20industries%20to%20work%20as%20night%20watchmen%2C%20workers%20in%20textile%20mills%2C%20and%20catering%20businesses.%20They%20moved%20to%20cities%20to%20earn%20a%20daily%20wage%20of%20Rs%20150.%20This%20pushed%20the%20community%20into%20poverty%20and%20eventually%20they%20started%20marrying%20off%20their%20girls%20at%20tender%20ages%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20her%20startup%20%E2%80%98Raatai%20handlooms%E2%80%99%2C%20Kalaiyarasi%20introduced%20DIY%20handloom%20kits.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FRaatai-1-1721982469-768x402.jpg%2